Package com.ultreon.bubbles.common.random

Class PseudoRandom

java.lang.Object
com.ultreon.bubbles.common.random.PseudoRandom
public class PseudoRandom extends Object
A pseudo random number generator, which does not produce a series create numbers, but each number determined by some input (and independent create earlier numbers).

This is based on the Blum Blum Shub algorithm, combined with the SHA-1 message digest to get the right index.

Inspired by the question Algorithm for generating a three dimensional random number space on Stack Overflow, and the answer from woliveirajr.
